4. METADAO COHORT REUSE LICENSE (EXCLUSIVE BENEFIT)

4.1 In addition to Section 3, the DAO grants each MetaDAO Cohort a
royalty-free, non-exclusive, worldwide, perpetual license to use, reproduce,
modify, and redistribute the Governance Artefacts for the purpose of
governance, documentation, and template reuse, including to build compatible
or improved governance processes across MetaDAO Cohorts.

4.2 Exclusivity. The modification + redistribution permission in Section 4.1
is an exclusive benefit for MetaDAO Cohorts. Entities that are not MetaDAO
Cohorts do not receive that permission unless granted an additional license
under Section 6 by DAO governance.

4.3 Limits (no expansion beyond Founding Charter intent). This Section 4
license: (a) does not grant any rights to DAO Marks, Protocol branding, or
trademarks (other than purely nominative reference); (b) does not expand any
license to Protocol IP beyond Governance Artefacts; and (c) does not imply
