Repository Materials do not constitute a license to deploy, operate,
support, or provide any Implementation of Protocol IP.

5.3 No Implementation / Strategy License. This License does not grant any
rights in or to any Production Implementations (including any concrete
rebalancer or trading mechanism implementation), whether or not described
by a state machine, diagram, specification, parameter schema, pseudocode,
or other Governance Artefact.
For avoidance of doubt: the license to Governance Artefacts permits
reuse of the descriptive materials (e.g., state machines), but does not
license any corresponding implementation unless that implementation is
itself included in the repository and expressly labeled as non-production
reference tooling.

5.4 No MetaDAO IP License. This License does not grant rights to deploy,
operate, commercialize, or provide services using MetaDAO IP. Nothing herein
is a sublicense of MetaDAO rights.

5.5 No Misrepresentation. You must not present Repository Materials (or modified
versions) as official, adopted, ratified, or effective DAO instruments unless
they are, in fact, adopted in accordance with the Company Agreement and clearly
identified as such.

Where applicable, Tertiary Instruments (including SOPs) are official/effective
only to the extent adopted or ratified through the DAO's governance process
(including by Resolution and, where applicable, by an Operational Pack under the
SOP: Order of Business for Operational Packs), and identified with the required
status/version/effective-date metadata.

Publication in a repository, inclusion in a branch, draft status, pull request,
issue, discussion thread, or hash reference does not by itself make any item an
official, adopted, ratified, or effective instrument.

If you publish modified versions where permitted, you must clearly mark them as
modified and not official.

5.6 No resale / commercialization (survives derivatives). You must not sell,
license for a fee, monetize access to, or otherwise commercially exploit the
Repository Materials or any derivatives or compilations of them (including
