collections), except with an additional license granted under Section 6.
For avoidance of doubt, this prohibition includes charging for access to a
fork, mirror, or hosted copy of the Repository Materials (whether or not
the underlying repository is otherwise publicly accessible).
This restriction applies even if modifications are substantial.

